# Task 1 â€“ Number Game

->Description
This is a console-based Number Guessing Game developed using Java.

The system generates a random number between 1 and 100.  
The user has limited attempts to guess the correct number.

-> Features
- Random number generation
- Limited attempts
- Multiple rounds option
- Score tracking
- User feedback (Too High / Too Low / Correct)

-> Technologies Used
- Java
- Random class
- Loops
- Conditional statements


